led silently on local.\n\nYou can set environment variable `ROUTE_IP` or set options `host` to forward metrics report, if you want to view the data when develop on local. [This document](https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service/blob/master/packages/consul/README.md#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96-boe-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84-ip-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80) will help you to get valid agent IP.\n\nIf you got any alarm on BOE because metrics report on local, you can set environment variable `METRICS_ENABLE=false` to make metrics library NOT send report to server(agent).\n\nActually, the `METRICS_ENABLE` will only effect SEND, you can also get log on local-dev by set options `debug: true`.\n","files":["lib","index.js"],"types":"lib/index.d.ts","repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service"},"dist":{"integrity":"sha512-djLTHb45IEzceM8roMcApjgdsJccQfpWcyIHVTT3Gh873HTJL3KznM+uFVAGynPmAvMTojNFTI0m7/popaYslQ==","shasum":"8e4b4b5c4ac50f8cdec8b25579df291b6a5215e1","size":14397,"tarball":"https://bnpm.byted.org/@byted-service/metrics/-/metrics-2.0.0-alpha.0.tgz","unpackedSize":49068,"fileCount":21},"readmeFilename":"README.en.md","version":"2.0.0-alpha.0","_nodeVersion":"14.20.0","_npmUser":{"name":"nodejs-team","email":"nodejs-team@bytedance.com"},"license":"MIT","dependencies":{"@byted-service/env":"^1.15.0","@byted-service/netpool":"^1.1.1","tslib":"^1.9.3"},"maintainers":[{"name":"liyubei","avatar":"https://s3-fs.pstatp.com/static-resource/v1/bf5207f4-07f4-4c43-9004-b01af1aff365~?image_size=72x72&cut_type=&quality=&format=png&sticker_format=.webp","email":"liyubei@bytedance.com"},{"email":"nodejs-team@bnpm.com","name":"nodejs-team","avatar":""},{"avatar":"https://s1-fs.pstatp.com/static-resource/v1/d27d000e276d58ace3df~?image_size=72x72&cut_type=&quality=&format=png&sticker_format=.webp","email":"ouyangyadong@bytedance.com","name":"ouyangyadong"},{"avatar":"https://ee.bytedance.net/ratak/employees/3863359/avatar/?format=noop.png","email":"q